{
  "chapter": 293,
  "chapter_summary": "师妃暄将徐子陵引至成都北郊独尊堡，交待任务后飘然离去。管家方益民热情接待徐子陵，带他穿过堡内幽深景色来到侧园小楼。徐子陵见到石青璇，她遵守诺言展露真容，清丽绝伦令人屏息。石青璇请徐子陵继承岳山的霸刀与换日大法心得，目的是让他假扮岳山诱出天君席应——一个害得岳山家散人亡的宿敌。石青璇解释席应练成至高心法后狂妄自大，公然宣布毁寺以引宋缺前来，而岳山的手下败将正是他渴望出现的对手。徐子陵答应在成都逗留七天学习扮岳山的技巧。与此同时，寇仲独自乘船南下赴岭南，一心只想见宋玉致一面，感叹命运的不可逆料。本章以石青璇为徐子陵吹奏玉箫结束，两人情感渐深。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_fei_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "师妃暄",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "妃暄已完成任务，徐兄只要报上名字，自有人领徐兄往见青旋小姐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_fei_xuan",
      "text": "你不陪我进去吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_fei_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "师妃暄",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "青璇小姐怕不是那么欢喜见到我，但请勿追问原因，徐兄珍重。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "speaker_name": "方益民",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐公子大驾光临，实是我独尊堡的荣幸，请这边走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "speaker_name": "方益民",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们堡主到今早才知公子光临成都，又闻知巴盟的人有心留难公子，故立即找巴盟的奉振说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "text": "解堡主的隆情厚意，徐子陵非常感激。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "speaker_name": "方益民",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "是我们感激公子才真，请这边走。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "text": "你们因何要感激我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "speaker_name": "方益民",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "待会公子自会知晓，请恕小人不敢先行透露。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_min",
      "speaker_name": "方益民",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "公子请进小楼见青璇姑娘，小人告退。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "石小姐，徐子陵应约来哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "上来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "看到桌子上的东西吗？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "是否岳山仗之成名的霸刀呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "正是此刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "小姐的好意心领啦！一来我不爱挥刀弄剑，二来更怕背这么重的大刀奔波跋涉，小姐还是留来作纪念吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "没有它，你怎能扮岳山呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "以前我不也是没有它吗？连祝玉妍一时间都差点被瞒过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今次是不同的，祝玉妍只和岳山有一夕之缘，且由于她一向厌恶岳山，自然会设去忘记他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "今次？甚么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今次要骗的人是你另一死敌天君席应，只要有少许破绽，会立即给他看破，怎可不力求完美。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "见过小姐后，我立即离川，恐怕……唉！教在下该怎么说呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "看！连自己都知道过意不去哩！你弄坏人家和尚寺那么多尊罗汉，又从中学到没人能明白的神奇功夫，这么说走便走，不惭愧吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "子陵啊！你怎会是如此对别人苦难视若无睹的人呢？只有你扮成岳山，才可把席应诱出来，舍此再无其他妙计。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "小姐非不问世事的人吗？为何今次这么热心参与。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这恰好是青璇肩上负担之一，岳老临终前对宋缺已恨意全消，唯独对害得他家散人亡，更变得性情暴戾的天君席应念念不忘，假若子陵能为青璇和所有被害的人诛杀此魔，青璇会非常感激。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "好吧！连我自己都找不到拒绝的藉口，不过我确身有要事，只能在成都再逗留七天，期满我立即离开，小姐意下如何。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "七天是非常足够。首先你要依人家指点，把岳山扮得天衣无缝，最重要是你装成练得换日大法的样子，那纵使和真岳山有分别，别人都不会怀疑，皆因认识岳山的人均知他在与宋缺决战前，一直修练换日大法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "换日大法是否很厉害呢？若是如此，席应没理由送上门来给岳山试刀练靶的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "放心好啦。席应今次敢重返中原，因其练成了本门至高心法，再不把任何人放在眼内。如此公然宣布要毁寺，照我猜正是要把宋缺诱来，他又怎会怕宋缺的手下败将，他恨不得你出现才对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这是岳山晚年武功尽失的数十年间，闲来把霸刀和换日大法记录下来的心得，还旁及对一些人事的批评。嘻！这是你今天的功课呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不用苦起脸孔哩。人家会在这里陪你，把岳山生前的事迹巨细无遗的说与你知晓，保证你可扮得天衣无缝，不露任何破绽。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你仍未曾说呢。人家现在这样子好看吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 293,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    }
  ],
